txt.en: Thraknûl, once the most championed of torturers under the command of Sauron, still is able to capture and torture the most hardy warrior to ruin.
Challenge: Take a Turn on the Rack
Get captured by Thraknûl and defeat the prisoners in all of his cages
Thraknûl's main torture chamber houses many instruments of pain, as well as many holding cells for his victims.
